  "body": "> we need the personal_signTransaction: [tx, pw] function in geth in order to allow infura connection. The node is un-usable on a ordinary computer and the storage to large. SO its not really an options for Mist anymore\r\n\r\n> We want to add signing with the current geth for now, and for that we need the above function asap :smiley:\r\notherwise we would need to unlock, sign and lock, which causes a security risk, as the node is vulnerable for a few sec.\r\n\r\n> eth_signTransaction exists, but we needpersonal_signTransaction, which accepts a pw as second param\r\n\r\nvia @frozeman ",
